{"uuid": "8ed28ec9-fdce-4e30-936a-4bd191fa7bb0", "id": 1757, "date": "2018-04-23T05:00:25", "date_gmt": "2018-04-23T12:00:25", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=1757"}, "modified": "2019-04-14T11:59:50", "modified_gmt": "2019-04-14T18:59:50", "slug": "cover-me-it-takes-a-lot-to-laugh-it-takes-a-train-to-cry", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/04/23/cover-me-it-takes-a-lot-to-laugh-it-takes-a-train-to-cry/", "title": {"rendered": "Cover Me: It Takes a Lot to Laugh, It Takes a Train to Cry"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>Firing up the waaaaaayback machine today and travelling to Newark State College on May 15, 1971, so we can catch Dr. Zoom and The Sonic Boom performing Bob Dylan&#8217;s bluesy &#8220;It Takes a Lot to Laugh, It Takes a Train to Cry.&#8221;</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a great recording for its age, and you can even hear Steve introduce the song, and Bruce and Garry banter after it.</p>\n<div id=\"v-tLZCEiNE-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/tLZCEiNE?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p>Bruce&#8217;s version is decidedly fiercer than Dylan&#8217;s 1965 original:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bob Dylan - It Takes a Lot to Laugh, It Takes a Train to Cry (Official Audio)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SN1ACh8lzHg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>Performed just twice by the band in May 1971&#8211;as far as we know, Bruce hasn&#8217;t played it publicly since.</p>\n<p><strong>It Takes a Lot to Laugh, It Takes a Train to Cry</strong><br />\n<strong>First performed:</strong> May 14, 1971 (Asbury Park, NJ)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> May 15, 1971 (Union, NJ)</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Performed only twice, way back in 1971: Dr. Zoom and the Sonic Boom covers Bob Dylan&#8217;s &#8220;It Takes a Lot to Laugh, It Takes a Train to Cry.&#8221;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 1824, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [4], "tags": [803, 804], "class_list": ["post-1757", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-cover-me", "tag-bob-dylan", "tag-it-takes-a-lot-to-laugh-it-takes-a-train-to-cry"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/dylan.jpg?fit=358%2C354&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": 